customer gripping-chipmunk
-> floor[f1] :FloorAssignment
=> networkaddress @f1/c/1
=> userport 38118 RJ45
customer free-hyena
-> floor[f1] :FloorAssignment
=> networkaddress @f1/c/2
=> userport 27146 RJ45
customer fast-dragonfly
-> floor[f1] :FloorAssignment
=> networkaddress @f1/c/3
=> userport 64655 RJ45

## Floor 2
