# Infrastructure
## Floor 0
router 39915 RJ45[5] FIBER[5]
uplink DPUW FIBER
-> floor[f0] :FloorAssignment
-> port[39915/port6] :NetworkCableLinkFiber
uplink BCGO FIBER
-> floor[f0] :FloorAssignment
-> port[39915/port7] :NetworkCableLinkFiber
server 55153 FIBER[3]
port[55153/port0] -> port[39915/port5] :NetworkCableLinkRJ45

## Floor 1
uplink HYHH FIBER
-> floor[f1] :FloorAssignment
-> uplink[DPUW] :UplinkConnection

router 26564 FIBER[2] RJ45[3]
=> networkaddress @f1/r/1
-> floor[f1] :FloorAssignment
port[26564/port0] -> uplink[HYHH] :NetworkCableLinkFiber
port[26564/port2] -> customer[gripping-chipmunk]>userport :NetworkCableLinkRJ45
port[26564/port3] -> customer[free-hyena]>userport :NetworkCableLinkRJ45
port[26564/port4] -> customer[fast-dragonfly]>userport :NetworkCableLinkRJ45

## Floor 2
uplink MTVW FIBER
-> floor[f2] :FloorAssignment
-> uplink[BCGO] :UplinkConnection
uplink HAAJ RJ45
-> floor[f2] :FloorAssignment
router 86110 FIBER[2] RJ45[3]
port[86110/port0] -> uplink[MTVW] :NetworkCableLinkFiber
port[86110/port2] -> customer[same-millipede]>userport :NetworkCableLinkRJ45
port[86110/port3] -> customer[sparkling-stingray]>userport :NetworkCableLinkRJ45
port[86110/port4] -> customer[muddy-chihuahua]>userport :NetworkCableLinkRJ45
=> networkaddress @f2/r/1
-> floor[f2] :FloorAssignment
port[86110/port0] -> uplink[HAAJ] :NetworkCableLinkFiber
switch 8686 RJ45[5]
=> networkaddress @f2/sw/1
-> floor[f2] :FloorAssignment
port[86110/port4] -> port[8686/port0] :NetworkCableLinkRJ45